// figma.flow
// Minimal lifecycle for a pure MCP provider agent.
// Figma exposes tools to the Runtime — it has no autonomous conversational states.
// This file demonstrates that even server-style agents declare a .flow,
// even if its only role is to handle unavailability gracefully.

state init
  next responsive

state responsive
  on fallback
    guide "Figma MCP tools are unavailable in this environment."
    next responsive
